1
00:01:05,952 --> 00:01:08,384
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,512 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:14,359
The Empress Dowager has arrived.

4
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,680
Mother.

5
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,319
Xu Yu,

6
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,920
how dare you!

7
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,079
This is regicide!

8
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,640
Regicide warrants
the execution of your entire clan.

9
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,000
Aunt,

10
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,760
the Empress has always run wild

11
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:32,560
because of her powerful family.

12
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,519
- How insolent!
- You're the insolent one!

13
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:36,840
Thanks to His Majesty's
abundant blessings,

14
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,719
he didn't fall
for the Xu family's schemes.

15
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,680
What?

16
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,760
Your Xu family
has always been ambitious.

17
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:44,439
Now they're not even
bothering to hide it?

18
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:46,560
(Mother knows right from wrong.)

19
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,239
(Why condemn Xu Yu
without hearing the facts?)

20
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,799
(And Qiluo too.)

21
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,439
(She's merely a consort.)

22
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:54,000
(How dare she disrespect the Empress?)

23
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:56,200
His Majesty has arrived.

24
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:05,840
Your Majesty,

25
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,780
what brings you here?

26
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,199
Your Majesty.

27
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:16,159
Empress Dowager.

28
00:02:19,232 --> 00:02:19,960
Empress Dowager,

29
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,759
my fall into the water
wasn't the Empress's fault.

30
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:24,800
I've been unfilial and caused you worry.

31
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:26,560
Your Majesty,

32
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:29,000
Her Majesty bullied me.

33
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,479
Qiluo.

34
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,120
Your Majesty.

35
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:36,159
This is indecent.

36
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,240
Your Majesty.

37
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,680
Empress Dowager, don't worry.

38
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,039
I'll handle the Empress.

39
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,639
Return to your palace.

40
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:50,719
Qiluo,

41
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,520
accompany her.

42
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,240
Your Majesty.

43
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,520
Your Majesty.

44
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,560
What should we do, Your Majesty?

45
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,199
Your Majesty.

46
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,759
Don't twist my waist.

47
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,240
Then what do you propose?

48
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,479
Go find him.

49
00:03:15,808 --> 00:03:17,233
(Star-Gazing Pavilion)

50
00:03:18,653 --> 00:03:20,256
(Seven-day retreat. Do not disturb)

51
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,920
The Grand Preceptor is in retreat.

52
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,159
Who'll help us switch back?

53
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,879
Why would the Grand Preceptor
retreat now?

54
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:37,599
He has reasons for retreating.

55
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,680
Let's try solving this ourselves first.

56
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:54,639
(External force caused our body swap.)

57
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,639
(Let's try the same method.)

58
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,960
Your Majesty.

59
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:09,759
Are you ready?

60
00:04:12,288 --> 00:04:12,879
Come on.

61
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:18,279
Three, two, one!

62
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,319
Xu Yu,

63
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,040
you deceived me.

64
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,279
Your Majesty.

65
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:35,920
No.

66
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:38,040
We must abandon this method.

67
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,000
Otherwise, before swapping back,

68
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:41,399
we'll be exhausted.

69
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:44,040
I recall when we fell into the water,

70
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,360
I heard thunder.

71
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,879
There was indeed thunder.

72
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,560
My body felt a tingling pain.

73
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,600
What now?

74
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,639
Their Majesties jumped into water again.

75
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,319
It's time.

76
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:32,600
Where are you going?

77
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,639
To hold court.

78
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:35,879
Come back soon.

79
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,800
You're holding court.

80
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,800
I'm holding court?

81
00:05:49,216 --> 00:05:52,096
(Taiji Hall)

82
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:03,879
Your Majesty,

83
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,959
the imperial bloodline is fragile.

84
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:08,160
The crown prince position
remains vacant.

85
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:12,800
Without an heir soon,
ministers will grow restless,

86
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,839
and the realm cannot be pacified.

87
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:18,959
In my humble opinion,
concubine selection should be tomorrow.

88
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:22,759
(Maintain imperial dignity in court.)

89
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:25,680
Posture straight, gaze steady,

90
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,680
and never reveal joy or anger.

91
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,959
(My father fights at the frontier.)

92
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:36,160
(My brother postpones
marriage for the war.)

93
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,839
(You old fools)

94
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,879
(scramble to find
Xiao Jinyun concubines.)

95
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,680
(Treating me like decoration?)

96
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:47,959
With war raging, the treasury is empty.

97
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,680
This year's concubine selection
can be skipped.

98
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:55,839
Securing the imperial lineage
is the foundation of the state.

99
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,720
Provisions and supplies will be handled
by the Ministry of Revenue.

100
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:03,319
(How is this helping the Emperor?
It's clearly to sideline the Emperor.)

101
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,079
What do you mean?

102
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,399
Now our soldiers
are protecting the country,

103
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,840
fighting on the front lines.

104
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:14,001
Instead, I'll hold
a concubine selection.

105
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:16,400
Won't that make me
a pleasure-seeking tyrant?

106
00:07:18,801 --> 00:07:19,721
Cancel the selection.

107
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:20,840
That's all.

108
00:07:21,161 --> 00:07:21,801
Dismissed.

109
00:07:22,601 --> 00:07:24,361
- Your Majesty is wise!
- Your Majesty is wise!

110
00:07:24,361 --> 00:07:26,880
- We respectfully see Your Majesty off.
- We respectfully see Your Majesty off.

111
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,440
How dare you quibble!

112
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,880
Wasn't it you who pushed
His Majesty yesterday?

113
00:07:32,041 --> 00:07:35,280
Don't think you can hide it from me
because His Majesty favors you.

114
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:38,001
His Majesty has been
buried in memorials.

115
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,361
His body is exhausted.

116
00:07:39,721 --> 00:07:41,801
He slipped and accidentally
fell into the lake.

117
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:45,241
I jumped into the water to save him.

118
00:07:46,121 --> 00:07:49,080
Why did His Majesty fall into the water
as soon as he went to see you?

119
00:07:49,361 --> 00:07:50,721
Did you push him in

120
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:54,520
and then pretend to rescue him

121
00:07:54,681 --> 00:07:55,601
to vie for favor?

122
00:07:55,801 --> 00:07:57,121
I disdain such actions.

123
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,681
Nor would I be foolish enough

124
00:07:58,681 --> 00:08:01,161
to use such a risky move
to implicate my entire family.

125
00:08:01,921 --> 00:08:03,001
I've heard

126
00:08:03,481 --> 00:08:06,640
your family's recent border victories
are overshadowing the throne.

127
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,960
Who knows if you have ulterior motives?

128
00:08:09,601 --> 00:08:10,520
Heard?

129
00:08:11,121 --> 00:08:12,520
Then tell me, Consort Zhao.

130
00:08:12,681 --> 00:08:13,880
Where did you hear that?

131
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,721
You reside in the palace,

132
00:08:15,721 --> 00:08:17,921
yet you speak confidently
about the Xu family's affairs.

133
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:22,241
Could it be that Chancellor Zhao
informed you of court matters,

134
00:08:22,601 --> 00:08:25,440
using the harem to interfere in politics
and frame the Xu family?

135
00:08:26,801 --> 00:08:27,440
No.

136
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,440
Aunt.

137
00:08:33,361 --> 00:08:34,441
I'm exhausted.

138
00:09:01,151 --> 00:09:02,481
Is the Empress in Fengyi Palace?

139
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,481
A-A palace maid said

140
00:09:04,481 --> 00:09:06,400
Her Majesty went to Ci'an Palace
to pay respects,

141
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,760
and it's been some time.

142
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,241
(No. Could something have happened?)

143
00:09:10,841 --> 00:09:11,640
Your Majesty,

144
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,961
Prince Xiaoyao requests an audience.

145
00:09:13,961 --> 00:09:16,121
(Jinming, Prince Xiaoyao?)

146
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:21,640
(It's said that Prince Xiaoyao
is of noble character)

147
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,560
(and favored by the Emperor
and Empress Dowager.)

148
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:26,321
(He is elegant and handsome,)

149
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:30,441
(with a face like the autumn moon
and a glow like spring blossoms.)

150
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,441
So handsome.

151
00:09:36,321 --> 00:09:38,920
This is Prince Xiaoyao? So handsome.

152
00:09:49,729 --> 00:09:51,647
(Xiaoyao)

153
00:09:55,041 --> 00:09:57,345
(Xiao Jinming)

154
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,201
Jinyun.

155
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:13,880
Jinyun.

156
00:10:14,361 --> 00:10:15,920
Jinyun, lend me some money.

157
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,441
I've been cheated.

158
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,920
Prince Ning cheated.

159
00:10:20,721 --> 00:10:24,601
Jinyun, you almost
wouldn't have seen me.

160
00:10:24,601 --> 00:10:27,321
Jinyun.

161
00:10:27,713 --> 00:10:28,321
Brother!

162
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,040
You must avenge me.

163
00:10:33,601 --> 00:10:34,800
I'll issue an edict for you

164
00:10:34,944 --> 00:10:36,201
to seize Prince Ning's assets.

165
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,400
- Alright?
- Sure.

166
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,760
No, it's too severe.

167
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,160
Why go big for something small?

168
00:10:41,441 --> 00:10:43,321
Please, Jinyun, just lend me some money.

169
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:47,441
Lending you money is possible,
unless you agree to one condition.

170
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:49,721
What condition?

171
00:10:50,841 --> 00:10:53,001
Go to Ci'an Palace
and bring my wife back.

172
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:55,680
Rest assured,

173
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,441
I will not fail the mission.

174
00:10:58,241 --> 00:10:59,321
But, Jinyun,

175
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,800
you're quite concerned about her.

176
00:11:02,321 --> 00:11:03,760
Nonsense.

177
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,520
(I'm not concerned about him.)

178
00:11:07,841 --> 00:11:09,920
(I'm worried that if I don't
rescue Xiao Jinyun,)

179
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,361
(when we switch bodies back later,)

180
00:11:11,361 --> 00:11:13,640
(with his pettiness,
he will retaliate tenfold.)

181
00:11:15,841 --> 00:11:17,001
What are you waiting for?

182
00:11:17,001 --> 00:11:18,361
Go and bring her to Fengyi Palace.

183
00:11:22,361 --> 00:11:26,001
With me, Prince Xiaoyao,
stepping in, how could it not succeed?

184
00:11:30,241 --> 00:11:31,640
Jinyun.

185
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,560
Remember to prepare the money.

186
00:11:50,337 --> 00:11:55,521
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

187
00:11:56,257 --> 00:12:00,820
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

188
00:12:02,145 --> 00:12:07,560
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

189
00:12:08,129 --> 00:12:12,673
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

190
00:12:13,313 --> 00:12:18,577
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

191
00:12:18,945 --> 00:12:24,622
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

192
00:12:24,961 --> 00:12:26,977
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

193
00:12:27,169 --> 00:12:30,913
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

194
00:12:31,489 --> 00:12:36,161
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

195
00:12:36,705 --> 00:12:38,465
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

196
00:12:38,785 --> 00:12:42,401
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

197
00:12:42,648 --> 00:12:48,175
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
